<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog | Data & AI Insights</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4da6ff;
            --bg: #0a0b10;
            --card-bg: #161b22;
            --text-white: #ffffff;
            --text-gray: #a1a1a1;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text-white);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* NAVBAR */
        .navbar {
            padding: 20px 8%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(10, 11, 16, 0.98);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

        /* HEADER */
        .blog-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #111827, #0a0b10);
        }

        .blog-header h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* GRID SYSTEM */
        .blog-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        /* ARTICLE CARD */
        .article {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .article:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(77, 166, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .article img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            background: #222; /* Fallback if image fails */
        }

        .article-content { padding: 25px; }

        .article h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .article p {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .article ul {
            list-style: none;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .article li::before {
            content: "→ ";
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* QUOTE */
        .quote-container {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            background: #1e293b;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px dashed var(--primary);
        }

        .quote {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="navbar">
        <a href="index.html" class="logo">DATA & AI</a>
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html">Home</a>
            <a href="about.html">About</a>
            <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="blog-header">
        <h1>Blog Insights</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Exploring the future of technology and data.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="blog-container">
        <article class="article">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="AI">
            <div class="article-content">
                <h2>L'Avantage Décisionnel</h2>
                <p>Transformer la donnée brute en intelligence stratégique pour dominer votre marché.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Analyse prédictive</li>
                    <li>Optimisation des flux</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="article">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Data">
            <div class="article-content">
                <h2>Marketing & IA</h2>
                <p>Comment les algorithmes redéfinissent la relation client en 2026.</p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="article">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504639725590-34d0984388bd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Code">
            <div class="article-content">
                <h2>Compétences Clés</h2>
                <p>Les langages et outils indispensables :</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Python & SQL</li>
                    <li>Power BI</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </article>

        <div class="quote-container">
            <p class="quote">“La donnée seule ne vaut rien. Sa valeur naît lorsqu’elle guide une décision.”</p>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
